"geti2p.net/en/faq target=_blank rel=noreferrer>geti2p.net</a>"

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/help/troubleshoot_jsp.java:528
msgid ""
"You may also try <a href=irc://127.0.0.1:6668/saltR class=chatlink>#saltR</"
"a> or <a href=irc://127.0.0.1:6668/i2p-dev class=chatlink>#i2p</a> on I2P's "
